Package edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.io

Class StudentReader

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.io.StudentReader
public class StudentReader extends Object
StudentReader processes input CSV files that contain student information. Input CSV files should be in the following format: FIRST_NAME,LAST_NAME,UNITY_ID,STUDENT_ID,GPA,CREDIT_HOURS
